# Token Usage Gate

**Blocker:** Do not write hardcoded values in component SCSS without checking the token system first.

## 1. Token sources (check in order)

1. `apps/web/src/styles.scss` — colors, shadows, theme surfaces (`var(--primary)`, `var(--shadow-md)`, etc.)
2. `apps/web/src/styles/_typography-baseline.scss` — spacing, font sizes, radii, motion, line-heights, focus ring
3. `docs/design/tokens.md` — canonical reference with z-index ladder, elevation, and color semantics

## 2. Lookup table (common traps)

| Need | Use | Never |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Pill/circle radius | `var(--radius-full)` or `var(--radius-pill)` | `999px`, `9999px` |
| Panel/card radius | `var(--radius-md)`, `var(--radius-lg)` | `4px`, `8px` |
| Spacing/gaps | `var(--spacing-1)` through `var(--spacing-8)` | Raw `0.25rem`, `0.5rem` for gaps |
| Font sizes | `var(--font-size-2xs)` through `var(--font-size-2xl)` | Raw `0.8125rem`, `0.6875rem` |
| Transitions | `var(--motion-duration-fast)` (100ms), `var(--motion-duration-standard)` (150ms), `var(--motion-duration-slow)` (250ms), `var(--motion-duration-entrance)` (300ms) | Magic `120ms`, `180ms`, `200ms`, `300ms` |
| Easing | `var(--motion-ease-out)` | Raw `cubic-bezier(...)` |
| Z-index (product planes) | 0 / 100 / 200 / 300 / 302 / 400 / 500 / 501 | Invented values; undocumented layers |
| Shadows | `var(--shadow-sm\|md\|lg\|xl\|2xl)` | Hardcoded box-shadow composites |
| Menu/action hover bg | `var(--menu-item-hover)`, `var(--action-hover)` | `color-mix(in srgb, var(--primary) 8%...)` inline |
| Menu border | `var(--menu-border-subtle)` | `color-mix(in srgb, var(--border) 72%...)` inline |
| Menu/action text | `var(--menu-item-text)`, `var(--action-text)`, `var(--section-text)` | `var(--foreground)` / `var(--muted-foreground)` for themed rows |
| Sandstone theme overrides | `var(--sandstone-*)` globals from `styles.scss` | Inline hex (`#2f271f`, `#6b5a47`, etc.) |
| Colors | `var(--primary)`, `var(--foreground)`, `var(--border)`, `var(--muted-foreground)`, etc. | `var(--color-clay)`, `var(--color-*)` legacy names |

## 3. Allowed raw values (no token needed)

- `1px` borders and outlines (constitution-approved)
- `2px` focus rings
- `inset 0` / `0` for resets
- `100%` / `auto` / layout keywords

## 4. When a token is missing

If a value doesn't map to an existing token:
1. Check if a near-equivalent exists (e.g. `--spacing-3` = `0.75rem` instead of writing `0.75rem`)
2. If genuinely new, propose adding it to `_typography-baseline.scss` — do not invent inline values

## 5. Forbidden legacy patterns

- `var(--color-*)` — removed Phase 7; use semantic tweakcn names
- `var(--fp-*)` — removed
- `var(--overlay-rail-*)`, `var(--layout-sidebar-*)` — removed
- Hardcoded sandstone hex — use `var(--sandstone-*)` globals
- `:host-context([data-theme='sandstone'])` — **banned**; all theme variance lives in global interaction tokens
- Component-local `--mdv-*`, `--cde-*`, `--invite-*` var bridges — **removed**; use global `--menu-*` / `--action-*` tokens directly
